title: Ivan Rebroff
description:
Here are 2 rare Ivan Rebroff LPs which i mastered from my personal vinyl LP collection. I think they may be available online, i think i saw them once. But anyway, this is quite a treat for some of you who downloaded the Ivan rebroff torrents with the mixed songs which i also downloaded because i was looking for more of this Russian vocalist for my collection. I also scanned the cover art from the LPs.

Enjoy
